@startuml DeepSceneLoc_DFD_Level_1

!define PROCESS_COLOR #4A90E2
!define FUTURE_COLOR #FFA500
!define DATASTORE_COLOR #FFE4B5
!define ENTITY_COLOR #D3D3D3
!define TRAINING_COLOR #90EE90

' Title
title DeepSceneLoc - Data Flow Diagram (Level 1)\nMain System Processes

' === External Entities ===
actor User as user <<External Entity>>
actor Developer as dev <<External Entity>>
database "Places365\nDataset\n(50GB)" as places365 <<External Entity>>
cloud "Google Gemini\nAPI" as gemini <<External Entity>>

' === Main Runtime Processes (Blue) ===
rectangle "**Process 2**\nImage Preprocessing\n---\n• Resize 224x224\n• Normalize\n• Augmentation\n• To Tensor" as P2 PROCESS_COLOR

rectangle "**Process 3**\nStage 1: Scene Classification\n---\n• ResNet-50\n• 5 Categories\n• Confidence Scores" as P3 PROCESS_COLOR

rectangle "**Process 6**\nDisplay Results\n---\n• Format output\n• Show confidence\n• User interface" as P6 PROCESS_COLOR

' === Future Process (Orange - Dashed) ===
rectangle "**Process 4**\nStage 2: Exact Location\n---\n• Gemini AI\n• Landmark detection\n• GPS coordinates" as P4 FUTURE_COLOR #line.dashed

' === Training/Development Processes (Green) ===
rectangle "**Process 1**\nDataset Preparation\n---\n• Download\n• Validate\n• Split 70/20/10\n• Organize" as P1 TRAINING_COLOR

rectangle "**Process 5**\nModel Training\n---\n• Transfer Learning\n• Backpropagation\n• Checkpointing\n• Early Stopping" as P5 TRAINING_COLOR

rectangle "**Process 7**\nEvaluation & Metrics\n---\n• Test set inference\n• Confusion matrix\n• Accuracy, F1-score" as P7 TRAINING_COLOR

' === Data Stores ===
database "**D1**\nStructured Dataset\n---\ntrain/val/test\n~50GB" as D1 DATASTORE_COLOR

database "**D2**\nPretrained Weights\n---\nImageNet ResNet-50\n~100MB" as D2 DATASTORE_COLOR

database "**D3**\nModel Checkpoints\n---\nbest/latest/final\n~100MB each" as D3 DATASTORE_COLOR

database "**D4**\nTraining History\n---\nJSON logs\nloss/accuracy curves" as D4 DATASTORE_COLOR

database "**D5**\nEvaluation Results\n---\nMetrics, matrices\nReports" as D5 DATASTORE_COLOR

' ========================================
' === RUNTIME FLOW (Blue paths) ===
' ========================================
user --> P2 : Upload Image\n(JPG/PNG/JPEG)

P2 --> P3 : Preprocessed Tensor\n(1x3x224x224)

P3 --> P6 : Scene Category +\nConfidence (0-1)

P3 .down.> P4 : Scene Context +\nOriginal Image
note right of P4
  **Semester 2**
  (Weeks 11-13)
  Dashed = Future
end note

P4 .down.> P6 : Landmark, City,\nCountry, GPS

P6 --> user : Final Results\n(Stage 1 + Stage 2)

P4 .right.> gemini : API Query:\nImage + Context
gemini .left.> P4 : Location Data:\nJSON response

D3 -right-> P3 : Load\nbest_model.pth

' ========================================
' === TRAINING FLOW (Green paths) ===
' ========================================
places365 -down-> P1 : Raw Images\n(5 categories)

P1 -down-> D1 : Organized Data\n(folder structure)

D1 -right-> P2 : Training Batches\n(with labels)

P2 -down-> P5 : Augmented Tensors\n(batches of 32)

D2 -right-> P5 : Initialize Backbone\n(frozen layers 1-3)

P5 -right-> D3 : Save Weights\n(epoch checkpoints)

P5 -down-> D4 : Save Metrics\n(loss, accuracy)

' ========================================
' === EVALUATION FLOW (Orange paths) ===
' ========================================
dev --> P7 : Run Evaluation\nScript

D1 -down-> P7 : Test Set\n(10% of data)

D3 -down-> P7 : Trained Model\n(best_model.pth)

P7 -down-> D5 : Confusion Matrix,\nAccuracy, F1

D5 --> dev : Metrics Report\n(visualizations)

' ========================================
' === NOTES & ANNOTATIONS ===
' ========================================
note top of P3
  **Week 5 - Current**
  Infrastructure complete ✅
  Demo running on port 7860
  Full training in Week 6
end note

note bottom of P5
  **Transfer Learning**
  • Pretrained backbone (frozen)
  • Custom head (trainable)
  • Adam optimizer (lr=0.001)
  • Early stopping (patience=5)
end note

note right of D3
  **Checkpoint Strategy**
  • best_model.pth (highest val_acc)
  • latest_model.pth (most recent)
  • final_model.pth (after training)
end note

' ========================================
' === LEGEND ===
' ========================================
legend bottom left
  **Color Legend**
  |= Color |= Meaning |
  | Blue (Solid) | Runtime processes (Working) |
  | Green (Solid) | Training/Dev processes |
  | Orange (Dashed) | Future (Semester 2) |
  | Tan Cylinders | Data stores (persistent) |
  | Gray | External entities |
  
  **Status Legend**
  ✅ Complete / Working
  ⏳ In Progress
  🔜 Planned (Semester 2)
end legend

@enduml
